  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK684">
<l>aṟivuru vārāynta kalviyim mūṉṟiṉ</l>
<l>ceṟivuṭaiyāṉ celka viṉaikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He may go on a mission (to foreign rulers) who has combined in him all these three. viz., (natural) sense, an attractive bearing and well-tried learning.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
